<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>*Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Offer applicable to new ski bookings made between 8th February 2019 to 11pm on 12th February 2019.</li>
<li>Prices displayed on the web include the £100 per person saving.</li>
<li>Offer available on selected Chalet Hotels only, departing 23rd or 30th March 2019.</li>
<li>Offer <strong><u>not</u></strong> applicable to other properties or dates.</li>
<li>Prices are based on 7 night holidays, from the lowest priced departure point. Supplements for other flights/airports may apply.</li>
<li>All prices, offers and availability are correct at time of publishing, are subject to change &amp; availability and can be withdrawn at any time.</li>
</ul>]]></bodyText>
